Description: Tools for decomposing global value chain (GVC) participation and
    value-added trade using the frameworks proposed in Borin and Mancini
    "Measuring what matters in value-added trade"
    (Economic Systems Research, 35(4), 586-613, 2023,
    10.1080/09535314.2022.2153221>) and in Borin, Mancini and
    Taglioni "Economic Consequences of Trade and Global Value Chain
    Integration: A Measurement Perspective" (The World Bank Economic
    Review, 2025, 10.1093/wber/lhaf017>). The package provides
    functions to compute value-added trade measures and decompositions
    that follow these frameworks.
